## 🎯 Nästa Features - Höga Prioritet

### 1. **Dashboard Enhancements** ⭐⭐⭐ (Komponenter färdiga!)
**Status:** 🟡 Komponenter byggda men ej integrerade
**Uppskattad tid:** 2-3 timmar (komponenterna finns redan!)

**Färdiga komponenter:**
- ✅ KPICard.tsx (med AnimatedNumber, SparklineChart, trendpilar)
- ✅ ActivityHeatmap.tsx (GitHub-style heatmap)
- ✅ TagAnalytics.tsx (tag cloud + distribution chart)
- ✅ RadialProgressRings.tsx, KPIDetailDialog.tsx, SparklineChart.tsx

**Implementationsplan:**
- [ ] **Phase 1: Replace StatsCard with KPICard** (~30 min)
  - Import KPICard in Dashboard.tsx
  - Calculate trend data (compare to previous week/month)
  - Add sparkline data för varje metric (senaste 7 dagar)
  - Benefits: Animated counters, trend indicators, sparklines

- [ ] **Phase 2: Add Activity Heatmap** (~30 min)
  - Add ActivityHeatmap component under stats grid
  - Show last 90 days (3 months)
  - OnDayClick → filter tickets created that day
  - Benefits: Visual activity patterns, quick date filtering

- [ ] **Phase 3: Aging Tickets Widget** (~45 min)
  - Add new section: "Ärenden som kräver uppmärksamhet"
  - Show tickets open >7 days with no updates
  - Grouped by days: >7, >14, >30 days
  - Clickable cards to open ticket
  - Benefits: Prevents tickets from being forgotten

- [ ] **Phase 4: Recent Activity Stream** (~30 min)
  - Fetch ticket_history for last 24 hours
  - Display as timeline (user + action + time ago)
  - Limit to 10 items
  - Benefits: See what's happening across all tickets

**Exempel Dashboard Layout:**
```
┌─────────────────────────────────────────────┐
│ Dashboard                                   │
├─────────────────────────────────────────────┤
│ [KPI Grid] Open: 12 ↑2  In Progress: 5 ↓1  │
│            Waiting: 3 -  Resolved: 8 ↑3     │
├─────────────────────────────────────────────┤
│ [Activity Heatmap] Last 90 days             │
├─────────────────────────────────────────────┤
│ [Aging Tickets] 4 tickets need attention    │
│  • #142 (14 days) - Password reset          │
│  • #138 (12 days) - Network issue           │
├─────────────────────────────────────────────┤
│ [Recent Activity] Last 24 hours             │
│  🎫 #145 updated by Anton (5 min)           │
│  ✅ #143 closed by Admin (1h)               │
└─────────────────────────────────────────────┘
```

